{"section": "3.8.2: The components of an inductive proof.", "qid": 2, "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n <p>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <b>\n   Theorem:\n  </b>\n  For all n \u2208\n  <b>\n   Z\n  </b>\n  <sup>\n   +\n  </sup>\n  , Q(n) is true,\n  <br/>\n  <br/>\n  where Q(n) is a statement that is parameterized by a positive integer n.\n </p>\n <p>\n </p>\n</div>\n", "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <div class=\"setup flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"label\">\n   3)\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   If the inductive step says that for all positive integers Q(k) implies Q(k+1), then what is the inductive hypothesis?\n  </div>\n </div>\n <fieldset>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember119\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"Q(k+1)\" name=\"23\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember118&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    Q(k+1)\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember121\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"Q(n)\" name=\"23\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember120&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    Q(n)\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember123\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"Q(k)\" name=\"23\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember122&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    Q(k)\n   </label>\n  </div>\n </fieldset>\n</div>\n", "choices": ["<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember119\">\n <input aria-label=\"Q(k+1)\" name=\"23\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember118&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  Q(k+1)\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember121\">\n <input aria-label=\"Q(n)\" name=\"23\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember120&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  Q(n)\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember123\">\n <input aria-label=\"Q(k)\" name=\"23\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember122&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  Q(k)\n </label>\n</div>\n"], "answer": "Q(k)", "explanation": "<div aria-atomic=\"true\" class=\"explanation has-explanation correct\" role=\"alert\">\n <p class=\"message\">\n  Correct\n </p>\n Q(k) is the hypothesis of the conditional statement that Q(k) implies Q(k+1)\n</div>\n"}